{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:8","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:8","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:43","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":43,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" He went up on a mountain and sat there, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 7:31–37","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":31},{"label":"Mt 9:8","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":8},{"label":"Mt 18:8","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":8},{"label":"Mk 9:43","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":43}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:15:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and large crowds came to him, including the lame, the blind, the crippled, those unable to speak, and many others. They put them at his feet, and he healed them. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:15:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So the crowd was amazed when they saw those unable to speak talking, the crippled restored, the lame walking, and the blind seeing, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 29:23","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:68","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":68,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:17","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and they gave glory to the God of Israel."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 29:23","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":23},{"label":"Lk 1:68","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":68},{"label":"Ac 13:17","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:15:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Jesus called his disciples and said, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 14:14–21","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:1–10","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" “I have compassion on the crowd, because they’ve already stayed with me three days and have nothing to eat. I don’t want to send them away hungry, otherwise they might collapse on the way.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 14:14–21","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":14},{"label":"Mk 8:1–10","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:15:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The disciples said to him, “Where could we get enough bread in this desolate place "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:4","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 11:26","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:38","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" to feed such a crowd?”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 8:4","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":4},{"label":"2Co 11:26","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":26},{"label":"Heb 11:38","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":38}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:15:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“How many loaves do you have?” Jesus asked them."},{"kind":"text","text":" “Seven,” they said, “and a few small fish.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:15:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After commanding the crowd to sit down on the ground, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:15:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"he took the seven loaves and the fish, gave thanks, broke them, and gave them to the disciples, and the disciples gave them to the crowds. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:27","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":27,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 22:17","book":"Luk","chapter":22,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:11","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:23","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":23,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 27:35","book":"Act","chapter":27,"verse":35,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"cro